  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian Assistance for Assyrians in Lebanon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overall Goal: To improve the living conditions of Assyrian families living in Lebanon. 

Objective 1: To rehabilitate a space provided by the church to be used for support classes where the newly arriving children will be taught foreign languages required by the Lebanese curriculum;

Objective 2: To provide psychosocial and child protection activities will be implemented along the education activities to enhance the mental and psychosocial wellbeing of the children;

Objective 3: To provide Assyrian school age children with school kits to reduce the financial burden on their families.</narrative>
  </description>
